metadata.name: Carpe Diem #1
metadata.description:
With Carpe Diem (from Latin means “Seize the Day”), Zhannet Podobed invites viewers to reflect on the fleeting nature of time, and to make the most of every moment, and to find joy and purpose in every day.

This collection  is a powerful reminder that life is short, and that we should take every opportunity that comes our way. 

Zhannet Podobed's abstract artworks celebrate the beauty of the present, and remind us to live life to the fullest. 
 
Collaboration between Zhannet Podobed and AI Midjourney Collection has 32 artworks, 2000 x 2000 px / each
